title: MBB: Seniors Set to Lead Hawkeyes Into March
text:
MBB: Seniors Set to Lead Hawkeyes Into March 
Updated: Wed, Oct 07 2015, 10:00 PM 
Iowa basketball is back, and so are four key seniors. With their leadership, the Hawkeyes plan on making it back to the NCAA Tournament - and maybe more. Pat Moroney explains Iowa's edge in experience. 
  Ed Thomas Coach of the Week Faith, Family, Football. Words of Inspiration from the Coach Ed Thomas Foundation. CBS 2 and FOX 28 in partnership with the Eastern Iowa Airport are looking for coaches who embody the spirit of Coach Thomas by having a strong impact on the community and on the sidelines.
